{"tid":1946770,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"近日最9嘅兩項打J資訊，就係中國本土抗爭同外國反中熱潮","createTime":"2020-03-27T23:00:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-28T02:17:53.000Z","uid":31215,"like":19,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6f1cb9dfd5608f86861be7336c89b1854696f98c","tid":1946770,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T23:00:42.000Z","msg":"中國示威就算9數啦<br />\n中共一出手震壓/俾少少甜頭就十成十收皮<br />\n茂命示威、湖北示威邊次唔係咁<br />\n中共係未出手<br />\n一出手過幾日就冇野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n外國排華仲撚on9<br />\n個個post都有人話排華格局已成<br />\n打少陣J啦仆街<br />\n事實得台灣係一面倒排華，連美國都唔可以全面排華，其他國家直頭親中<br />\n講國內群眾，可能有一班人想打9中國，但左膠永遠佔多數<br />\n講國內政界，可能有個別議員/官員仇中，但政府大方向都係左膠/奶共，反中派勢力根本不及親中派<br />\n<br />\n得美國例外，但特朗普/參眾議員想全面對抗中共<br />\n班國內左膠、巨企同其他國家又唔配合<br />\nBill gates、apple、google、Elon musk 全部奶共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國bj中撚埋、意大利死咁撚多人、日本連奧運都搞唔成，都認清唔到自己敵人，唔反枱都算，仲要加強同中國合作，仲要繼續奶共<br />\n<br />\nG7竟然有G6連使用武漢肺災都覺得會傷害中國唔太好<br />\n屌你中國搞出黎嗰時有冇諗傷害你地唔太好呀<br />\n<br />\n聯合國世衞嗰啲國際組織又一面倒親中<br />\n<br />\n唔好再講咩話邊度邊度會唔會憎死中國，要排華<br />\n係唔會架<br />\n外國係on9到俾人殺一半人都唔識自動排華<br />\n反而越大鑊越想中國幫<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好再打J喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人亦未盡全力唱衰中共<br />\n之前幾千正評登報最後又搞唔死<br />\nTwitter 線人可以再多啲人"},{"pid":"7d3edea77be13046afbb05a8abb2688405313fa1","tid":1946770,"uid":297997,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T23:02:58.000Z","msg":"你老母就打飛機"},{"pid":"e869c4cadf08707faf5955e0b87e5144a9162d32","tid":1946770,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T23:06:33.000Z","msg":"美國帶頭就天下反㗎啦"},{"pid":"5eaf66b1c4ac25584d45ed7220db485bb73467fd","tid":1946770,"uid":297997,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T23:07:38.000Z","msg":"連自己都唔出聲<br />\n<br />\n邊撚個幫到你<br />\n<br />\nOn99"},{"pid":"ffa5167a68310490a587050fc2b27c2e53161542","tid":1946770,"uid":193233,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T23:25:06.000Z","msg":"講得岩，連登仔唔肯面對現實情何以堪"},{"pid":"1223c652b0c5a7e2c88eb1f1f9f08278568a0974","tid":1946770,"uid":147784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T23:27:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86941e6e0a13eaebfae3a415d31edba3f271d18d","tid":1946770,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ffa5167a68310490a587050fc2b27c2e53161542","tid":1946770,"uid":193233,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T23:25:06.000Z","msg":"講得岩，連登仔唔肯面對現實情何以堪"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T23:27:13.000Z","msg":"就係面對實情先要做"},{"pid":"c07dff0334a429c6cda7abe25be2be4dda60c240","tid":1946770,"uid":147784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T23:28:29.000Z","msg":"香港要同支那討價還價<br />\n就一定要學識不斷唱衰支那"},{"pid":"50e353942a424edf4af5d40c5e922de97659f3ab","tid":1946770,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c07dff0334a429c6cda7abe25be2be4dda60c240","tid":1946770,"uid":147784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T23:28:29.000Z","msg":"香港要同支那討價還價<br />\n就一定要學識不斷唱衰支那"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T23:30:17.000Z","msg":"同喚醒所有人<br />\n<br />\n唔通再坐定定等運到"},{"pid":"a338ff999276271f25ca760f953b81739df9f717","tid":1946770,"uid":147784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T00:18:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21cf3d